snippet.title: Mickey's Robot Laboratory Game - Mickey Mouse Game - Mickey's Robot Lab
snippet.description:
Mickey's Robot Laboratory Game - Mickey's Robot Lab from Disney

The factory is made up of the different sections shown on the left. Can you help put the pieces together to make your own original robot?

Like this video: Mickey's Robot Laboratory | Mickey Mouse Games
http://youtu.be/X_qFyEQv2qs

Subscribe To My Mickey Mouse Games Channel: http://www.youtube.com/user/themickeymousegames?sub_confirmation=1
